<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Share-Base Bond Certificate - NNL</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      background: #F4F1DE;
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .certificate {
      background: white;
      border: 8px solid #D4AF37;
      padding: 60px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #1B4332;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #1B4332;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .header h2 {
      color: #D4AF37;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .details {
      background: #F4F1DE;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #1B4332;
    }
    .details strong {
      color: #1B4332;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 2px solid #D4AF37;
    }
    .cert-number {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    @media print {
      body { padding: 0; }
      .certificate { border: none; box-shadow: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="certificate">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>SHARE-BASE BOND CERTIFICATE</h1>
      <h2>Namathu Natural Leader (NNL)</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>This certifies that <strong>{{ investment.firstname }} {{ investment.lastname }}</strong> has invested in a Share-Base Bond for the following agricultural production:</p>

      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Product:</strong> {{ investment.product_name }}</p>
        <p><strong>Investment Amount:</strong> â‚¹{{ investment.amount|number_format(2) }}</p>
        <p><strong>Profit Share:</strong> {{ investment.profit_share_percentage }}%</p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{ investment.duration }} days</p>
        <p><strong>Issue Date:</strong> {{ date_issued }}</p>
        <p><strong>Maturity Date:</strong> {{ maturity_date }}</p>
        <p><strong>Certificate Number:</strong> {{ certificate_number }}</p>
      </div>

      <p>This bond represents a direct investment in sustainable farming practices and entitles the holder to a share of profits from global export margins upon maturity.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">This certificate is issued by Namathu Natural Leader and is valid for the duration specified above.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Namathu Natural Leader (NNL)</strong></p>
      <p>Direct from India's Farmers to Global Markets</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
        Certificate generated on {{ "now"|date("F d, Y") }}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cert-number">
      Certificate #{{ certificate_number }}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    <button onclick="window.print()" style="background: #1B4332; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer;">
      Print Certificate
    </button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
